163
00:19:33,632 --> 00:19:36,101
Yeah, well, they always do.

164
00:19:36,501 --> 00:19:38,769
l saw them notices.

165
00:19:38,937 --> 00:19:40,571
It's different this time.

166
00:19:40,939 --> 00:19:42,807
