no doubt.

253
00:25:25,457 --> 00:25:27,625
No. No.

254
00:25:27,793 --> 00:25:30,028
l wouldn't try to pet them if l was you.

255
00:25:35,499 --> 00:25:36,900
I'm headed southeast.

256
